			<CASNumber>12125-02-9</CASNumber>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="en">Ammonium chloride is the salt of ammonia and hydrogen chloride, a colourless crystalline substance that is widely used in fertilizers, solids, and medicine. It is a mineral and electrolyte that treats low chloride levels in the blood and metabolic alkalosis. It is also used in dry cells and as an expectorant. It is formed as the by-product in the manufacturing process of sodium carbonate and has diuretic effects.</common:generalComment>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="zh">氯化铵是氨和氯化氢的盐，是一种无色结晶物质，广泛用于肥料、固体和医药。它是一种矿物质和电解质，可治疗血液中氯含量低和代谢性碱中毒。它还可用于干燥细胞和祛痰。它是碳酸钠生产过程中的副产品，具有利尿作用。</common:generalComment>
